## Project Overview
<!-- Fill this in: What is this project? What does it do? -->
This is a command-line todo manager built with TypeScript.

## Key Commands
- `npm run start` — Run the CLI
- `npm run test` — Run tests with Vitest
- `npm run lint` — Type-check with TypeScript

